Description: USED Fender Classic Player Jazzmaster Special - 3-Color Sunburst (196) Physical ConditionThis Fender Jazzmaster guitar is in excellent condition with only a few light signs of use. There's one small ding on the rear of the body as well as some light smudges in the finish about the edges. Aside from this the guitar only exhibits some light tarnishing about the hardware. Great sounding and playing guitar! FretwearThis guitar has virtually no wear on the frets. Plays great! ActionAction is low but could use a quick tweak to your liking! ElectronicsAll electronics work properly! CaseNo case or gig bag included!
